0364.name: Chrysalimon
0364.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0364.leader_skill: Medium increase in the support power of all allies.
0364.profile: An adult Digimon with the appearance of a chrysalis. The child Digimon Keramon temporarily becomes a chrysalis and conserves its energy in order to evolve into a stronger Digimon.

0370.name: Angewomon
0370.main_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0370.leader_skill: High increase in the attack power of yellow holy allies.
0370.profile: A Digimon with a calm personality, but very strict with twisted and evil characters. She will punish them until they will change. Thanks to her morals and power, she is praised as 'The Goddes' of the Digital World.

0388.name: Keramon
0388.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0388.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense power of purple dark allies.
0388.profile: A child Digimon that thinks that destroying data is just a game. He destroys the computers he penetrates, eating away data at a rate of 100MB per second.

0411.name: Patamon
0411.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0411.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0411.profile: A Digimon that can fly in the sky due to his big ears. However, his speed is only 1 km/h, so it is faster if he walks. He doesn't wear a Holy Ring, but inside him lie hidden genes of ancient Digimon.

0412.name: Bancholeomon
0412.main_skill: Damages all enemies while your HP drops to 1.
0412.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of red dragon allies.
0412.profile: A Digimon who continued to win respecting his spirit of justice and without having to break his beliefs. He would face even the Three Great Angels or the Royal Knights if this would help him make his spirit of justice understood.

0436.name: Devimon & Ladydevimon
0436.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0436.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of all allies.
0436.profile: Two Fallen Angel Digimon dressed in black. They have sly and atrocious personalities but superior intelligence!

0437.name: Angemon & Angewomon
0437.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0437.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of all allies.
0437.profile: These Digimon have gentle personalities but are very composed when it comes to punishing evil. They attack the enemy until they destroy it!

0438.name: Devimon & Lady Devimon
0438.main_skill: Only purple dark cards will appear next.
0438.leader_skill: Halves the damage received from yellow holy enemies.
0438.profile: Anniversary limited scenario! Two Fallen Angel Digimon dressed in black, with a sly and atrocious personality, but superior intelligence!

0439.name: Angemon & Angewomon
0439.main_skill: High decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0439.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of yellow holy allies.
0439.profile: Thank you for preregistering! These Digimon have gentle personalities, but are very composed when it comes to punishing evil. They attack the enemy until they destroy him!

0444.name: Lunamon
0444.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0444.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in green nature cards.
0444.profile: A Digimon born through the fusion of lunar observation data. Its big ears make it look like a rabbit. It is timid and gets attached easily. It can also wield abilities connected to the power of darkness.

0445.name: Lekismon
0445.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0445.leader_skill: Some green nature, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0445.profile: A Beast Man Digimon with amazing, powerful jumps. It has its enemies at its mercy with its fast moves. It has a very elusive personality, making its appearance somewhat mysterious.

0446.name: Crescemon
0446.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0446.leader_skill: Only green nature cards will appear next.
0446.profile: A Demon Man Digimon. It fights its enemies with its flexible body and supple moves. It always fights in an elegant way, and it is said that its power increases considerably under the moonlight.

0447.name: Dianamon
0447.main_skill: Reduces the damage received by half.
0447.leader_skill: Adds a big delay to all enemy attacks.
0447.profile: One of the Olympos XII. It presides over water and ice and can act even when the surrounding temperature is absolute zero. Like the moon, it is two-faced and hides a terrible power under its beauty.

0448.name: Dorumon
0448.main_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0448.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense of all allies.
0448.profile: A beast Digimon with an old-style interface on its forehead. It is speculated it is an experimental 'prototype Digimon' from before the Digimon were discovered.

0449.name: Dorugamon
0449.main_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0449.leader_skill: Medium increase in the defense of all allies.
0449.profile: A ferocious Beast Dragon Digimon. It has the attributes of both beasts and dragons. Many Digimon start running away as soon as they see its shadow.

0450.name: Doruguremon
0450.main_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 2.
0450.leader_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0450.profile: A Beast Dragon Digimon of huge size. Its nickname is 'the Final Enemy'. Its form was released through the interface on its forehead by the life-data of the legendary creature 'the Dragon'.

0451.name: Alphamon
0451.main_skill: Changes the value of all cards to 9.
0451.leader_skill: Huge increase in the defense of all allies.
0451.profile: One of the Royal Knights. It is also called 'the Aloof Hermit'. It wears a blue fluttering cloak, and its place is called 'the Empty Seat'.

0452.name: Vajramon
0452.main_skill: Some blue knight, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0452.leader_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0452.profile: A Digimon who seeks to find the truth about the physical and spiritual worlds. It is under the command of Xuanwumon, one of the Four Holy Beasts.

0453.name: Gaioumon
0453.main_skill: Only blue knight cards will appear next.
0453.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of all allies.
0453.profile: A Dragon Man Digimon. It is a subspecies of the Greymon species. It is excellent as a combat species, and its becomes more powerful whenever it wins a battle.

0454.name: Zanbamon
0454.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in blue knight cards.
0454.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of all allies.
0454.profile: A Digimon who likes to fight directly with the enemy. It is a general who always stands in the vanguard of its army.

0455.name: Guilmon
0455.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0455.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0455.profile: A fighter Digimon comparable to a carnivorous beast. It hides in itself the inherent potential of Digimon. It can become a protective presence in the Digital World if its power is correctly exercised.

0456.name: Growmon
0456.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0456.profile: A wild and ferocious Digimon. It is called 'the Deep Crimson Demon Dragon'. Its roar has the power to shake the ones who hear it, and its mouth spits burning flames. Depending on the tamer's level of training, it can also fight in the name of justice.

0457.name: Megalogrowmon
0457.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0457.leader_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0457.profile: A huge Cyborg Digimon whose upper body is covered in Chrome Digizoid. It can also fly using the verniers on its shoulders, making it immensely powerful in both terrestrial and aerial combat.

0458.name: Dukemon
0458.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0458.leader_skill: Only green nature cards will appear next.
0458.profile: A Digimon born from Megidramon. Its name is also linked to the Royal Knights. Its weapons, Gram and Aegis, form from its armor, which is made completely of Chrome Digizoid.

0459.name: Gomamon
0459.main_skill: Small decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0459.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0459.profile: A naughty Digimon that likes pranks. Its body is covered with fur so that it can resist cold temperatures. Its claws help it break hard blocks of ice. When it gets angry, the red hair on its head bristles.

0460.name: Ikkakumon
0460.main_skill: Medium decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0460.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0460.profile: A Digimon with a horn made of Mithril. The skin under its fur is as hard as its horn. Its claws emit a high temperature which melts the ice under its feet, secures it on firm ground, and allows it to act even in extremely cold places.

0461.name: Zudomon
0461.main_skill: High decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0461.profile: A materialistic Digimon that protects its honed body with leather and armor stolen from its enemies. It also possesses the Thor Hammer, a Chrome Digizoid weapon dug out of ancient ice, which produces violent shock waves when used.

0462.name: Plesiomon
0462.main_skill: Huge decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0462.leader_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0462.profile: A Digimon that rarely shows itself. It appears to be surrounded by mist, disturbing the viewer's vision. With its white body and refined appearance, it is a very mysterious figure.

0463.name: Vikemon
0463.main_skill: Huge decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0463.leader_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0463.profile: A Beast Man Digimon in the ultimate form. It governs permafrost, the land of extreme cold. Its fur has crystallized, and it's said to now be as hard as Chrome Digizoid.

0464.name: Coronamon
0464.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0464.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in red dragon cards.
0464.profile: A Digimon born from sun-watching data. It has a strong sense of justice and is an innocent, naive character. It is good at direct fire attacks, and it can also release flame bombs.

0465.name: Firamon
0465.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0465.leader_skill: Changes all the blue knight cards in brown recovery cards.
0465.profile: A Beast Digimon with the nickname of 'the Lion soaring in the sky'. It is a careful leader, protecting a certain relic of the Digital World.

0466.name: Flaremon
0466.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0466.leader_skill: The blue knight cards will not appear.
0466.profile: A majestic Beast Man Digimon. Its mane and presence make it look scary at first glance. However, it has great strength of will and fights through any difficulty for the sake of its friends.

0467.name: Apollomon
0467.main_skill: Inflicts most of the damage to all enemies.
0467.leader_skill: Only red dragon cards will appear next.
0467.profile: One of the Olympos XII. It has in its body a fiery energy with the power to purify all that exists. Its boiling blood and its pride give it the strength to control this fierce energy.

0468.name: Omegamon
0468.main_skill: Reduces the damage received by half.
0468.leader_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0468.profile: A Holy Knight Digimon born through the fusion of miracles by the will of the good ones. Well-rounded in combat, it effortlessly wields weapons that themselves have the strength of two Digimon.

0496.name: Imperialdramon FM
0496.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0496.leader_skill: Some red dragon, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0496.profile: A Digimon who unleashed its full power in dragon mode and transformed into a legendary dragon warrior. It is incredibly intelligent and capable of controlling its violent power.

0498.name: Paildramon
0498.main_skill: Big increase in the attack power of all allies.
0498.leader_skill: Some red dragon, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0498.profile: A Digimon who jogress-evolved from XV-mon and Stingmon. Although it has the skilled attacks of dragons and the defensive ability of insects, the dragon attributes are a little stronger. It is very loyal and always protects its master.

0500.name: Ceresmon
0500.main_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0500.leader_skill: Slightly reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0500.profile: A Digimon with a peaceful appearance. It can control plant Digimon and absorb the enemy's energy using its terrifying skill, Famis.
